author: Xbox
description:
Styx is missing.

No snark. No footsteps in the rafters. No loot mysteriously disappearing.
Just… silence. And that’s honestly the scariest part.

But today, the shadows finally talk.
The Release Date Trailer reveals when the world’s sneakiest (self-proclaimed, but come on…) goblin crawls back into the spotlight:
Styx returns on February 19, 2026.

Slip once more into the grimy boots of Styx and lead your crew through a crumbling empire built for betrayal, blades, and very poor workplace safety standards.

Outsmart, outstab, and outsteal your enemies.
Explore 3 towering environments crafted for vertical stealth.
Chase Quartz, because power, war, and shiny things are always worth the trouble.

This isn’t just a comeback. It’s a warning:
A single goblin with a dagger can still ruin everyone’s day.

Styx: Blades of Greed launches February 19, 2026 on Xbox Series X|S.

https://www.xbox.com/games/store/styx-blades-of-greed/9NZTKVTDZ2LB

author: Xbox
description:
Let vengeance lead you to victory during Season 20: Vendetta!

A new villain steps into the spotlight with the arrival of our first official melee Damage Hero, Vendetta. With unmatched mobility, devastating close-range power, and a hunger for domination, Vendetta fights to reclaim her father’s legacy with deep ties to Talon and the next chapter of Overwatch 2’s global story.

Stadium levels up once again with Doomfist and Wuyang stepping into the arena, and the arrival of a brand new China Control map. We’re also giving players a rank reset and new rewards to chase as they keep climbing up the leaderboards.

Deck the halls as you brawl with the wintery cosmetics in the Season 20 Battle Pass. And with the 80 Mythic Prisms you’ll earn, bring some western flair to your festivities with the new Divine Desperado Cassidy Mythic Skin.

Winter Wonderland is back with a magical twist on a fan-favorite mode! Enjoy Mischief & Magic on a festive-themed map and with fun holiday props. And on week
title: Overwatch 2 | Season 20: Vendetta Official Trailer
